OL,3,CGuernsey's Standards Commissioner
OL,4,Cresigns
OL,6,FGuernsey's Commissioner for Standards
OL,7,Fhas resigned from her post, following
OL,8,Fpoliticians voting against her
OL,9,Frecommendation that a former Chief
OL,10,FMinister should be suspended.
OL,12,FDr Melissa McCullough explained her
OL,13,Freasoning, saying that "a Commissioner
OL,14,Fcannot uphold standards in a system
OL,15,Fwhere standards are not seen to be
OL,16,Fupheld."
