OL,3,CGuernsey's Standards Commissioner
OL,4,Cresigns
OL,6,FShe found Deputy Gavin St Pier, who is
OL,7,Fnow the Vice-President of Policy and
OL,8,FResources, to have broken the States'
OL,9,FCode of Conduct for talking to a
OL,10,FGuardian reporter about families'
OL,11,Fsafeguarding complaints related to
OL,12,Flocal Dr Sandie Bohin.
OL,14,FShe said that independent reviews
OL,15,F"have consistently found no wrongdoing
OL,16,Frelated to Dr Bohin's clinical
OL,17,Fjudgement or her actions" and the
OL,18,Fallegations are "extremely serious and
OL,19,Funfounded".
