OL,6,FShe added that "misleading public
OL,7,Fcommentary and misinformation" may
OL,8,Fhave had an "undue influence on
OL,9,FDeputies".
OL,11,F"For clarity, my investigation focused
OL,12,Fsolely on the conduct of Deputy St
OL,13,FPier as complained about.
