OL,3,CGuernsey's Standards Commissioner
OL,4,Cresigns
OL,6,F"The complaint concerned the
OL,7,Fconfirmation of unsubstantiated and
OL,8,Fseriously misleading information to a
OL,9,Fjournalist, information that was
OL,10,Fsensitive and harmful to the
OL,11,Freputation of the complainant and
OL,12,Factions which the complainant alleged
OL,13,Fwas furtherance of a vendetta against
OL,14,Fher.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
