OL,3,CGuernsey's Standards Commissioner
OL,4,Cresigns
OL,6,F"Where an Assembly decides not to
OL,7,Fsuspend despite two independent
OL,8,FCommissioners' recommendations, this
OL,9,Fcan signal to the public that the
OL,10,FAssembly is unwilling to enforce
OL,11,Fconsequences and ensure
OL,12,Faccountability, that Deputies are
OL,13,Fprioritising political considerations
OL,14,Fover standards and that the
OL,15,Findependent process has limited real-
OL,16,Fworld effect.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
