OL,3,CGuernsey's Standards Commissioner
OL,4,Cresigns
OL,6,F"Equally, if after exhausting an
OL,7,Findependent appeals process and whilst
OL,8,Fawaiting the public debate on the
OL,9,Fsanction, a Deputy can campaign
OL,10,Fpublicly and undermine the process and
OL,11,Fits findings in the media, and face no
OL,12,Fconsequences for undermining the
OL,13,Fsystem, it sends a message that others
OL,14,Fcan do the same."
OL,16,FDr McCullough was appointed as the Pan
OL,17,FIsland Commissioner for Standards in
OL,18,FMarch 2023.
